@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

title System Sequence Diagram (SSD) - Search Figure catalogue

autonumber

actor "Show Designer" as SD
participant ":System" as System

activate SD

activate System

    SD -> System: login()
    System --> SD: authenticated

    deactivate System
    SD -> System: ask to search for figures

    System --> SD: request data (id, name, categoryId, availability, customerId,...)
    deactivate System
    SD -> System: types requested data (id, name, categoryId, availability, customerId,...)

    activate System

    System --> SD: show all data registered for confirmation
    deactivate System

    SD -> System: searchFigures(id, name, categoryId, availability, customerId,...)
    activate System

        System -> System: validations(...)
        activate System

        deactivate System

        System -> System: findFiguresByFilter(id, name, categoryId, availability, customerId,...)
        activate System


        System --> System: figureList
        deactivate System


    System --> SD: show the output of public figure list
    deactivate System
deactivate SD

@enduml
